reviewText: I wanted this disc of shorts for the Ginger Rogers episode, and I am so pleased with the quality of the whole that I would say it is well worth the effort of finding this dvd and buying it.

There was no description of this collection, other than Edward Everett Horton's name, so I was hoping that he would be in all of them.  Unfortunately, the only EEH short was Ask Dad, which I'm happy to have, so it was worth purchasing. The other shorts here are unremarkable.
